        <item>
            <title>2.2.10</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 14:41:01 -0400</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/hoomanaskari/mac-dictate-anywhere</link>
            <sparkle:version>21</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.2.10</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# Dictate Anywhere 2.2.10

- Added OpenAI-compatible transcript cleanup for local and self-hosted servers such as LM Studio, llama.cpp, vLLM, and LocalAI.
- Improved FluidAudio custom vocabulary handling by using FluidAudio vocabulary boosting for the final transcript.
- Fixed final transcription capture so stopping recording keeps the last spoken words.
- Improved pasted transcript spacing so separate dictations are separated cleanly.
]]></description>
